OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with late evening sunshine for
OL,7,Fmany but cloudier in the west near the
OL,8,Fcoast. Dry with clear intervals
OL,9,Fovernight, staying mostly cloudy in
OL,10,Fthe west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAnother dry day with long
OL,13,Fsunny spells away from western coasts,
OL,14,Fwhich remain rather cloudy. Feeling
OL,15,Fwarm in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
